---
title: Double Moroccan Honey Chicken & Zesty Veggie Couscous with Currants & Lemon Yoghurt
description: We love the way honey caramelises in a pan, lending a crispy, sticky finish to chicken. We’ve gone for chicken breast steaks here, because they pack a fantastic flavour, remain moist as they cook and complement the bed of delicious roast veggie couscous that comes with them.

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with pearl couscous due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6682281c004ad21ab42e4718-c86bb4f4.jpeg
